Package com.fasterxml.storemate.shared.hash

Package that contains core hashing interfaces and implementations of StoreMate.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlockHasher32  
    BlockMurmur3Hasher
    Class that calculates full Murmur3 checksum for given data, using standard Public Domain implementation from https://github.com/yonik/java_util/blob/master/src/util/hash/MurmurHash3.java
    HashConstants  
    IncrementalHasher32
    Base class for hashers that can work in incremental fashion, that is, where content is sent via one or more calls to IncrementalHasher32.update(byte[], int, int), before final hash value is calculated.
    IncrementalMurmur3Hasher
